0_16	0.091145222	The move has been controversial, however, as many groups have raised concerns that insects will become resistant to Bt, which would seriously hurt organic farmers who are permitted to use Bt insecticides as their only emergency pest control option.
0_17	0.092054448	An EPA spokesman defended the agency's decision.
