7_19	0.13574463	Processed food that is made from at least 95 percent organic ingredients could also carry the seal.
7_20	0.13376781	And processed food containing at least 50 percent organic ingredients could be labeled ``made with organic ingredients'' and list up to three of them.
7_21	0.23210292	Irradiation, genetic modification and the use of sludge would be prohibited not only in the organic ingredients but in the conventional ingredients in foods made partly with organic ingredients.
7_22	0.11703136	Products made with less than 50 percent organic ingredients may use the word organic only in the list of ingredients on the side panel; in this case, the prohibition against those three processes would not apply.
