13_6	0.083547831	Turning apples into applesauce or tomatoes into tomato paste reduces levels significantly.
13_7	0.038631147	Freezing produce has virtually no impact.
13_8	0.082054288	Another reader wondered if peeling vegetables reduced the pesticide level.
13_9	0.08275518	Generally, peeling fruits and vegetables will reduce the level, but some pesticides are systemic and taken up through the roots.
