13_26	0.076231241	In my version, which is given below, there is no guar gum, used as a thickener.
13_27	0.089395583	Because blue cheese has such a strong flavor, not much is needed, and that keeps the calories and fat down.
13_28	0.08841417	This dressing is delicious on ripe tomatoes or Belgian endive and as an alternative to the usual dressing for coleslaw or potato salad.
13_29	0.087966183	To make enough for four people, mash two ounces (four tablespoons) of blue cheese with six tablespoons of plain nonfat yogurt, two tablespoons of brandy and a couple of pinches of cayenne.
13_30	0.092042401	Mix well.
13_31	0.074175879	The dressing will keep for a week or two in the refrigerator, tightly covered.
